accessibility.text: Its features include High Sensitivity to gas, stable for long time, simple drive circuit, fast response and many other.
It is mainly used for gas detection.
In this project MQ6 is used as an input device to measure the amount of gas present in the air.
There are series of MQ sensors which are used for the detection of different gases.
Its cost is about Rs.160 and is easily available at any electronics store.
